title: Ted Greene discusses Wes Montgomery 2
description: RARE video footage of Ted Greene giving a guitar lesson filmed in August of 1998. Ted discusses writing the Guitar Player Magazine article on Wes Montgomery, and also comments on Wes' playing style. Video Credits: Nick Stasinos
